
Steps for making the upgrade package

1:server_config.mk:
      modify ota_url and server_url
2:make upgrade package:
      make ota

Steps for making the upgrade bin

1: make

Directories and files
.
├── board_config.mk
├── include
│   ├── common.h
│   └── config.h
├── Makefile
├── out
│   └── README
├── partitions.tab
├── README
├── server_config.mk
├── src
│   ├── mkupdate.py
│   ├── nv_area.c
│   ├── nv_ro_demo.c
│   ├── partition.py
│   ├── read_partition.c
│   ├── test.c
│   ├── unzip.sh
│   ├── update.c
│   └── wr_flag.c
└── src_image
    ├── update_fs.cramfs
    ├── user_fs.cramfs
    └── xImage

board_config.mk
	this config is for wr_flag update
	if you want modify board info,only fix it
	      for example: every partition name, nor blocksize

server_config.mk
	this config is for mkupdate.py
	if you want modify url ,only fix it
	      for example: ota url, server url

partitions.tab
	This file was generated by partition.py.
	It is for mkupdate.py
	if you want modify partition table ,only fix partition.py
src
	This directory to store the source code

src_image
	This directory to store the update image
